<div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="card shadow">
        <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
            <h2 class="h4 mb-0">Vendor Research</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p class="lead">Research vendor information from external sources</p>
            
            <form action="/vendors/research/search" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group mb-3">
                    <label for="searchTerm">Search Term</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="searchTerm" name="searchTerm" 
                        placeholder="Enter company name, domain, or keyword" required>
                    <small class="form-text text-muted">More specific terms will yield better results</small>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group mb-3">
                    <label for="source">Data Source</label>
                    <select class="form-select" id="source" name="source">
                        <option value="web" selected>Web Search</option>
                        <option value="crunchbase">Crunchbase (Premium)</option>
                        <option value="linkedin">LinkedIn (Premium)</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-search me-1"></i> Search Vendors
                </button>
                <a href="/vendors" class="btn btn-outline-secondary ms-2">Cancel</a>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card shadow mt-4">
        <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
            <h3 class="h5 mb-0">About this tool</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>The vendor research tool helps you discover information about software vendors and their licensing options without manual research.</p>
            
            <h4 class="h6 mt-3">Available Sources:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Web Search</strong> - General information from across the web</li>
                <li><strong>Crunchbase</strong> - Detailed company data (requires premium subscription)</li>
                <li><strong>LinkedIn</strong> - Professional company profiles (requires premium subscription)</li>
            </ul>
            
            <div class="alert alert-info mt-3">
                <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>
                Results from web searches are for reference only. Always verify information with the vendor directly.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div> 